From: art-suite conda packaging
Subject: [PATCH] DatabaseSupport.cc: include <cassert> for assert()

DatabaseSupport.cc calls assert() (line 23) but never includes <cassert>.
Older libstdc++ pulled it in transitively via other standard headers; newer
libstdc++ (conda-forge GCC) does not, so the build fails with
"'assert' was not declared in this scope". Add the explicit include.

--- a/fhiclcpp/DatabaseSupport.cc
+++ b/fhiclcpp/DatabaseSupport.cc
@@ -4,6 +4,8 @@
 #include "fhiclcpp/ParameterSet.h"
 #include "fhiclcpp/ParameterSetRegistry.h"
 
+#include <cassert>
+
 void
 fhicl::decompose_fhicl(std::string const& filename,
                        std::vector<std::string>& records,
